data.description: Explore the luxurious comfort and style in this magnificent 4-bed, 2 full/2 half bath center hall colonial home. An open layout affords seamless movement on the main level. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a sizable center island, seamlessly linking to the living room and sunroom. Enjoy the private deck accessible from the sunroom, great for hosting gatherings. Upstairs, discover four bedrooms, notably the primary suite featuring a generous bathroom with a dual sink vanity, walk-in shower, and soaking tub. The finished basement provides extra space and opens to the backyard. Additionally, gutter guards and downspouts, linked to a French drain, have been installed. Don't miss your chance to experience this exceptional home firsthand!
